                    <h1 class="panel-title"><b><h4 align="center">Tic-Tac-Toe Game</h4></b></h1>
                </div>
                <div class="panel-body">
                    <h5 class="center"><b>RULES</b></h5>

                    <ol type="1">
                        <li> The Game is Played on 3*3 matrix (i.e 3 Squares by 3 Squares )</li>
                        <br>
                        <li> You are X , and Computer is O .</li>
                        <br>
                        <li> Player take turns putting their marks in empty squares.</li>
                        <br>
                        <li> The first player to get 3 of his marks in a top , down ,across or diagonal is the
                            winner .
                        </li>
                        <br>
                        <li> When all the 9 square are full , the game is over. If no player has 3 marks in a row then
                            the game is tie .
                        </li>
                        <br>
                    </ol>
                    <h5 class="center"><b>Enjoy the Game</b></h5>
                </div>
